				<td colspan="2"><span>The Bard you saw was most likely chant or swarm kiting those trees. Their melee range is too large to allow you to effectively AoE kite them without dieing. Give up on the trees, move to PoV golems or undead, PoN ravens or nightstalkers... The trees are just too much hassle for what they give exp wise until you get the 64 charm.</span></td>
