				<td colspan="2"><span>I use:
<br />

<br />
62- MoM
<br />
59- DB
<br />
2- CoD
<br />
18 - DDD
<br />

<br />
I can't use SCC because it does not stack with MoM because they both slow.  After pulling I've usually been beat up a bit and sing a heal song with the first 3 (all string) ignoring DDD until I'm full health.  Once full health I add the DDD although it does only in the 20's for me without a brass equipped.  I'm not to the point that I can swap out instruments while manual AoE.... yet.  I need to get a Ruj lute so can use my 1.8 brass mace secondary with a primary lute.  I used to swap out while auto AoE but I'm too lazy now.  Whenever my Puretone comes available I turn it on during a kite and can usually work a lug AoE down a lot faster as Puretone lasts about half a kite.  
<br />

<br />
Not related per say, another thing I have that I just love is a custom container that splits the slots apart and adds primary and secondary between them.  I can store all my weapons and instruments in a bag and it makes for quick swapping.  Got it off EQGUI a long time ago.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> </span></td>
