				<td colspan="2"><span>Just a little trick I used to help learn aoe kiting.  In Dulak on the boats if you run around the mast (or rather the wooden base) of the boat you will be in AoE range.  Just watch out for the very first boat there is a log or barrel that can make you get stuck.  This is with run3, not sure how it would work with a different run speed (ie Selo's).</span></td>
